Unveiled Auroral Breakup - Dancing Lights in Canada's Extreme North

Nature Documentary hosted by Laura Post, published by NHK broadcasted as part of NHK Great Nature series in 2012 - English narration

Information
------------------------------

On a dogsled journey through the magnificient scenery of the far north of Canada, in the "auroral oval," we attempt to film an aurora outburst, when lights in seven colors explode across the sky.
